verbose_text: In order to investigate the role of reactive oxygen species (ROS) in LicA induced autophagy, ROS, glutathione (GSH) and O 2 - were measured in LicA treated HCCs, and antioxidant N-Acetyl-L-cysteine (NAC) was cotreated with LicA in HCCs, then mechanisms of ROS induced autophagy was investigated in LicA or LicA combined with NAC treated HCCs.
